{"tid":974740,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"墨爾本亞裔客瘋搶奶粉　超市被迫下架","createTime":"2019-01-09T06:08:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-09T07:41:04.000Z","uid":75969,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"279388e6ddc806dc94c53b90ee589cb1a95b5e53","tid":974740,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T06:08:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190109/s00005/e96c32ba9d52cab4c385b74dbc4587cd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190109%2Fs00005%2Fe96c32ba9d52cab4c385b74dbc4587cd.jpg&h=8695322a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n澳洲墨爾本一間超市近日發生亞裔顧客瘋搶嬰兒配方奶粉事件，從現場片段所見，場面極混亂，有關超市只好從貨架收起奶粉。有當地母親對事件感到非常困擾及憤怒。<br />\n<br />\n有關超市位於墨爾本主要亞裔社區箱丘（Box Hill），隸屬連鎖超市品牌沃爾沃斯（Woolworths）。網上片段所見，當時一大群亞裔顧客聚集在超市一條通道前搶購奶粉，情況相當混亂。<br />\n<br />\n當地電視台報道，箱丘沃爾沃斯超市為避免混亂繼續，只好從貨架上收起奶粉。而深入調查後，發現有關情況不止出現在箱丘，整個墨爾本都有類似現象。<br />\n<br />\n沃爾沃斯超市發言人表示，顧客和員工安全是公司首要考慮，而該等哄搶行為明顯不能接受。<br />\n<br />\n有當地母親受訪時表示，對此感到非常憤怒，指她家附近超市的奶粉早已搶購一空，情況已持續超過一個月，她要每晚駕車前往全墨爾本各家超市，求購所需奶粉。她兒子更曾因無奶可飲而不斷嚎啕大哭，令她感到壓力甚大，非常困擾。<br />\n<br />\n去年10月，亦曾有類似情況出現，沃爾沃斯超市當時把原本每人限買10罐奶粉，減至2罐。<br />\n<br />\n亞裔社群去年12月於墨爾本箱丘超市搶購短片<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/tDQeNfoj1C0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FtDQeNfoj1C0&d=FTypIbPskK5BqgetbecOisVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=be5d9354\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/tDQeNfoj1C0</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/國際/article/20190109/s00005/1547005970249\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2Farticle%2F20190109%2Fs00005%2F1547005970249&d=FTypIbPskK5BqgetbecOisVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=3646aafd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2Farticle%2F20190109%2Fs00005%2F1547005970249&h=fcab32a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/國際/article/20190109/s00005/1547005970249</a>"},{"pid":"ac9e2a806a29f4843c0c0620fe458975f5d95fe4","tid":974740,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T06:22:59.000Z","msg":"限買到冇油水賺D支那人就唔搶架啦"},{"pid":"8ee751b6eea080266f5feab5215512879d767cd5","tid":974740,"uid":200328,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T06:27:56.000Z","msg":"支那生蕃係要去到邊柒到邊<br />\n周圍搶晒人啲奶粉<br />\n根本應該限制成國生蕃唔比去其他地方<br />\n困狗咁困"},{"pid":"43aa70160800b825356a51b7821715c190767647","tid":974740,"uid":39365,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T06:30:19.000Z","msg":"所以排華係有其原因既"},{"pid":"eb0d3063ea062203ea26f515dc76fc02f6a235bd","tid":974740,"uid":152476,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T06:31:13.000Z","msg":"亞乜野裔<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4591e2f9cbfe15cd7a388c9d503d308205d87f08","tid":974740,"uid":57376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"eb0d3063ea062203ea26f515dc76fc02f6a235bd","tid":974740,"uid":152476,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T06:31:13.000Z","msg":"亞乜野裔<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T06:40:20.000Z","msg":"我都睇到屌出聲<br />\n有著數就華裔<br />\n柒人柒事就亞裔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18165c08f8e81a3ff0c3b2f2cc1e80cda52bc343","tid":974740,"uid":997,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T07:06:53.000Z","msg":"支那人就支那人啦<br />\n亞裔<br />\n<br />\n屌晒你班5毛記者全家"},{"pid":"a5874b75e67550ce0808480bb22617e69612ddde","tid":974740,"uid":129739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T07:08:10.000Z","msg":"支持澳洲興起民粹政黨，行限奶令政策，加入侵侵反中包圍網<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44a16b5ee75b041919518057868bc